00:11:13.679 --> 00:11:14.960
I suppose it's my fault.

00:11:15.639 --> 00:11:16.759
I raised the child...

00:11:17.000 --> 00:11:18.240
...to be too responsible.

00:11:18.919 --> 00:11:19.720
Mom.

