00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:02.200
Don't even think of making excuses.

00:12:02.519 --> 00:12:03.440
At the very least...

00:12:03.440 --> 00:12:05.120
...let your dad and me, in our lifetime...

00:12:05.159 --> 00:12:07.559
